org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters

Class ImpinjDetailedVersion

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.llrp.ltk.types.LLRPParameter
      • org.llrp.ltk.types.TLVParameter
        • org.llrp.ltk.generated.parameters.Custom
          • org.llrp.ltk.generated.custom.parameters.ImpinjDetailedVersion
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AccessCommandOpSpec, AccessCommandOpSpecResult, SpecParameter

    public class ImpinjDetailedVersion
extends Custom
    This custom parameter provides detailed information about the individual components running on the Reader. The primary platform version is available in the FirmwareVersion field in the GeneralDeviceCapabilities parameter of the Reader's capabilities. However, there are sub-components of the Reader that contain independent version information that is unavailable in this manner. This parameter provides this detailed information. See also
